-- Germany’s Labor Minister Wants Higher Wages, Bild-Zeitung Says
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 2012-02-11T10:53:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-11/germany-s-labor-minister-wants-higher-wages-bild-zeitung-says.html
Germany ’s Labor Minister Ursula von der Leyen wants pay to rise faster than inflation after German
companies generated profits and workers tempered wage-increase
demands in past years, Bild-Zeitung reported, citing an
interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
